(1935, '区四星高中共同体高一数学期中分析会在我校召开', '5月2日上午，区四星高中共同体高一年级全体数学老师齐聚我校，召开期中分析会，区教研员练育红主持了本次会议，我校高一主管黄爱民副校长、高一年级组孔德高主任参加了活动。\n\n会议前，大家观摩了我校孙盼盼老师在高一（2）班开设的一节课《棱柱·棱锥·棱台》。\n\n然后，集中评课，大家畅所欲言，肯定了孙老师观摩课的优点，也提出了商榷性意见；进行期中分析，丁沟中学、大桥中学、仙城中学高一数学备课组长田广庆、田长平、王二林老师借助翔实的数据，分别分析了成绩与不足；最后，区教研员练育红就区四星高中共同体的深度发展、下阶段高一数学的教学工作，做了指导性发言。\n\n本次分析会的召开，为我区四星共同体高一数学教学下一步工作打下了坚实的基础。（ZGX）', '年级组', '2018-05-03', 'http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfk7ztQHLxaSeVEgx4PMpKdWx4ic0Mp9XbEYvECbvHpVnF7TGtzXnPy4Mw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfk4BpDPibSPcib8FN3M5KgSEEmHazpmf7olydRGOuxSGJrjuiaQA6Ffr5oQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkXknaTF4mYg4ibVvOOicWeEqfkrmUibf4U8HmaJ3Qx4Dcib3cibWyHwh7mfA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkOtvkNsibfxf1Pf3wSALrFKx3tomIEciak7OnHYln8H45cyWkYoB1RFsg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkToiclJoXSSBkb7lxg6NfGKWk9x4p9B5hjnDOc2ZiaGdS7ia26wvJCBD7w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkXjHgUmJPnoPgcKhvrtwo8budzzwfTvHiacFERvU69FUMXLX8htvpjcQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkIusQkQnQ4I74HgHjA4zEpz8hOicib4ZefkKKCVPm4hPCEWicPGibNc1sSg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkKO6oLWvaiaULG1vz2OmibVJr77ATCcnbQr9NXBoJjH32cPsImibXkafdA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkb7CFLGw2aNiayIgZI8ONYzPAfjIrMlibGIiaKx8vwPZtrnDLgnfznGicHg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkxfsZyPotIRyTGjVdyxibkBz4AqnTHMttwbFsFdTCFen02KjPXX1sVicQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkEhjSeZmVUjIjvegBvXXtGZHricdKCnqhM0ydicPa2KuHysbYORTbxujg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfk1jhz6Y1ib4eQcPcA7Eicf4ObTnf7YxEmXqCkAmA2vIE3otzAbFVbZrgA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkoO6f2QwK98VMqhhJ1yOtI2IHrXfSAbRcic9O1icCE4OibW3HghBZvjwaw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkyFQzERrib43BGIU2gibKHFevQRR4ZEJTTO4E08MDLgWXaQbnNEcDgLkQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkNlOxIqAP5MJC3lz2Y3VaKWofS02ONvYra3tuHurSK6WrQxvFxyP0Kw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkKJUTiaTgwRvBk6hoFqfibAUPT2xdh4fx0wKpdwsXnxb9aicud8TpXaaZg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkh1fkTg4CNIoaHoa1ZfsicjE9JGRMeibG1ZVKw6GGJqT09wPoTgnBQg8g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkQWg7fK2qUzqsIicFbNE9XsfdiazkFkuf5RpHbZlDTzVWIFRvPwQe65wQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkUoO4b1ZH6TojPicGIcZvAuXWfSjWpkBDshdszFSM23glRkRxXGyGWIg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkUs6BI4sCDUcCEH4tcHPSoK7CPRP1AAMUibAOZFMYuicOXKze4KlyLFYA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| ', NULL, '丁中高一家校讲堂', NULL, '校园新闻'),
(1936, '表彰先进，鞭策落后——高一召开部分学生座谈会', '期中考试成绩已经揭晓，各种数据均已产生。为了及时总结本次考试的得失，更好地迎接下阶段的学习，5月2日晚7点，高一年级组召集部分学生召开座谈会，刘立忠校长做主题报告，年级主管黄爱民副校长主持会议，年级组孔德高主任、李亚军副主任参加会议。\n\n会上，刘立忠校长选读了期中考试中进步较大、成绩较好的部分同学名单，对这些同学予以了热情的表扬，鼓励他们再接再厉；对成绩有所退步的同学，进行了未点名地批评，希望这些同学有所警惕。接着，着重讲了以下内容：一、相信自己，付出就有回报；二，态度端正，态度决定高度；三，明确目标，目标引领进取；四、刻苦努力，珍惜点滴时间，抵得住诱惑；五、处理好课堂与课后的关系，课堂确保效率，课后及时巩固所学知识，及时解决问题。\n\n\n\n最后，黄爱民副校长要求同学们不忘初心，担负使命，牢记刘立忠校长的谆谆教导，认真学习，以优异的成绩报答父母。（ZGX）\n\n\n\n\n\n', '年级组', '2018-05-02', 'http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfk1TgFxPbRAegsRkVtHx35UhA3PPttbMc3WFVgZ4Qch92PIH8cRAc5Gg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkagLZ1A0iatNRlWV6wgib1oSN3icnGibx9siav2pF98weU9soicufHibjBlSicg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkVr8W0WWnrgFdmuItmFKlyGfsZNuxbXWhqzuHcroYsblXVhYNaLBEHg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkjmHIOGDBibE7lIopBBqe5TmE5O67looKEm5ejdzcuIOaGMPCMBnQKeg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfk7fYfhzsTtvvIMzWtvrJqgKrTbPrxeCONUlqamsht8iaGJMcr0YX3QEQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkBPlnAwlowFIoGa5GicWH1TloVPibnduHJRXr8icZNXrXmPHiaaxpC74WVg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkTia8fiag4XnHD5b7BtDvTFtTtGnKNxYia7uuxGvMTVxJ9K4E4M8LkaYiaw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfk1LW4ia0NFPMGtgJOfb8EvkI5t1lNnOYRbEdQ625gMuU7ZFK5mLiaONoQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfk0G1o2Z2pC6DYzcEPeic94AXNiaL7Tm7icW3LxoI0JZTnTriaCMhibrZ2crw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkWtAydSmYm1Ly1agwcu0cYJiaVIlaOiaayLNJ3LVEfLd8AmCK1I6KtvEQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg||| https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wmiahnG0wzAaZV2dibNIkNCnuGibl9icsOfkdtoQWu2dGyF8wUHvYba2ukQIib36Q